nt assumptions fail. By aligning robustness and alignment objectives, our method enables more reliable zero-shot transfer without relying on parallel data, dictionary induction, or post-hoc mapping techniques. We expect this to significantly outperform existing robust training methods in both accuracy and consistency across diverse language families.",
